---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/layout/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/layout/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service | Stockade"
  description="Read Stockade's Terms of Service. By using our free trading simulator you agree to these terms. No real money, no financial advice."
>
  <Navbar />

  <main class="max-w-[760px] mx-auto px-6 py-16">

    <div class="mb-10">
      <div class="text-[11px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[#f59e0b] mb-3">Legal</div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[var(--c-text)] mb-3">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-[13px] font-mono text-[var(--c-text-subtle)]">Last updated: June 22, 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose-legal">

      <section>
        <h2>Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>
          By accessing or using Stockade ("the Service") at stockademarketsim.com, you agree to be bound by these
          Terms of Service. If you do not agree to any part of these terms, you may not use the Service.
          We reserve the right to update these terms at any time; continued use of the Service after
          changes constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Description of Service</h2>
        <p>
          Stockade is a <strong>free, browser-based stock and cryptocurrency trading simulator</strong>.
          The Service is intended for educational and entertainment purposes only. All trading on
          Stockade is conducted using virtual, simulated money with no real-world monetary value.
          No real assets, currencies, or financial instruments are purchased, sold, or transferred
          through the Service.
        </p>
        <p>
          Stockade does not require registration and can be used immediately by anyone with a
          compatible web browser. Your simulation data is stored locally in your browser and is not
          held on our servers.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Not Financial Advice</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>Nothing on Stockade constitutes financial, investment, legal, or tax advice.</strong>
          The Service is designed solely to help users learn about trading mechanics in a risk-free
          simulated environment. Any strategies, techniques, or results observed within the simulator
          do not represent advice to trade real financial markets, and past simulated performance is
          not indicative of future real-world results.
        </p>
        <p>
          You should consult a licensed financial adviser before making any real investment decisions.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Permitted Use</h2>
        <p>You may use the Service for lawful, personal, non-commercial purposes. You agree not to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Use the Service for any unlawful purpose or in violation of any applicable laws.</li>
          <li>Attempt to reverse-engineer, scrape, or systematically extract data from the Service.</li>
          <li>Introduce malware, viruses, or any malicious code into the Service.</li>
          <li>Misrepresent simulated results as real trading performance for commercial gain or to
              mislead others.</li>
          <li>Use automated bots or scripts to interact with the Service in a way that disrupts its
              normal operation.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Virtual Currency</h2>
        <p>
          The virtual balance (starting at $100,000 USD equivalent) provided within the simulator has
          absolutely no monetary value and cannot be withdrawn, transferred, exchanged, or redeemed for
          real money or any other asset. Accumulating virtual profits within Stockade confers no
          financial rights or entitlements whatsoever.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <p>
          The Service is provided on an <strong>"as is"</strong> and <strong>"as available"</strong>
          basis without warranties of any kind, either express or implied, including but not limited
          to implied warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, or
          non-infringement. We do not warrant that the Service will be uninterrupted or error-free.
        </p>
        <p>
          Simulated price data used in Stockade is generated algorithmically and does not represent
          real market prices. Any resemblance to actual market movements is coincidental.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          To the fullest extent permitted by law, Stockade and its operators shall not be liable for
          any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use
          of, or inability to use, the Service — including but not limited to any financial losses
          incurred in real markets as a result of strategies tested on the simulator.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Termination</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to suspend or discontinue the Service at any time, with or without
          notice, for any reason, including maintenance, updates, or permanent closure. Since no
          account or personal data is held on our servers, there is no data to delete upon termination.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Governing Law</h2>
        <p>
          These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with applicable laws, without
          regard to conflict of law provisions. Any disputes arising from these Terms or the Service
          shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the competent courts in the applicable
          jurisdiction.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about these Terms of Service may be sent to
          <a href="mailto:hello@stockademarketsim.com">hello@stockademarketsim.com</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose-legal {
    color: var(--c-text-muted);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .prose-legal section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-border);
  }
  .prose-legal section:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .prose-legal h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--c-text);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  .prose-legal p {
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
  }
  .prose-legal ul {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0.9rem 1.4rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }
  .prose-legal li {
    list-style: disc;
  }
  .prose-legal a {
    color: #f59e0b;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
  .prose-legal a:hover {
    color: #fbbf24;
  }
  .prose-legal strong {
    color: var(--c-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
